<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Time Log Correction Notice</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #111;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: #111111;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      opacity: 0.75;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .success-box {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .success-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #111;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .success-box p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      color: #444;
    }
    .info-card {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    }
    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
    }
    .info-value {
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .notice {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-left: 4px solid #111111;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .notice p {
      margin: 0 0 6px 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .notice p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #111111;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #888;
      font-size: 12px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      body { padding: 10px; }
      .header { padding: 20px; }
      .header h1 { font-size: 22px; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .info-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Time Log Correction</h1>
    <p>{{companyName}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong>,</p>

    <div class="success-box">
      <h3>Your time log has been corrected</h3>
      <p>We identified an issue where our system incorrectly auto-clocked you out on <strong>{{originalDate}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>This has been corrected — your session has been reopened and your supervisor has been notified to finalize your clock-out time.</p>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin: 30px 0 15px 0;">Affected Session</h3>

    <div class="info-card">
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Clock-In Time:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{clockInTime}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Incorrect Clock-Out (now removed):</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{incorrectClockOutTime}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Status:</span>
        <span class="info-value">Reopened — Pending Supervisor Review</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="notice">
      <p><strong>What happens next:</strong></p>
      <p>Your supervisor will review and set the correct clock-out time.</p>
      <p>No action is required from your end. If you have any concerns, please reach out to your supervisor or HR.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/employee/punch-logs" class="button">View My Time Logs</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; color: #444; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>What went wrong?</strong> A system error caused certain sessions to be automatically
        closed before the correct conditions were met. We have fixed the issue and corrected all
        affected records. We apologize for any inconvenience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated notification from BizBuddy.</p>
    <p>© {{currentYear}} BizBuddy LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #999;">
      If you have any concerns, please contact your supervisor or HR department.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
